creator: Interact Software
descriptionHtml:
Connect with colleagues on the go, access all your important work information and keep up-to-date with the latest news from within your business. Introducing Moss: bringing you the best of your Moss intranet, straight to your Android device.

View current news in your mobile homepage, read your favourite blogs, and keep links to your most needed content handy. With push notifications straight from the Moss app, be confident of never missing an important update or message. Moss keeps you informed, no matter where you’re working.

Using Moss’s Enterprise Search, you can instantly access all your vital business documents and storage: giving you the information you need, when you need it. You’ll also get access to your company People Directory on the move, with the ability to search colleagues and call or email directly from the app.

Moss supports all existing authentication modes used by your intranet (SAML / LDAPS / Local Directory) meaning setting up your Moss app is quick and simple. Simply use your existing credentials, and you’re good to go. With Moss, you’re connected to your business – even when out of the office.
descriptionShort: With Moss, you’re connected to your workplace – even when out of the office.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Magic Links: You can now log in by using your email address or mobile phone number
• Bug fixes and general performance improvements

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
